FBIS3-37106 "drsov030_m_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-030 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Feb 1994 Tajikistan Russian Helicopter Crashes; `Considerable Human Losses' LD1302182894 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1600 GMT 13 Feb 94 LD1302182894 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] A MI-8 helicopter belonging to a Russian border troops unit had an accident at about 1300 Moscow time [1000 GMT] while carrying out a medical flight in the region of the settlement (?Shurabad) in Tajikistan. There are considerable human losses. A commission has been set up under the deputy commander in chief of border troops to investigate the causes of the accident. That was a report from a Mayak correspondent.
